WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.500
Afterparty Forge 2045 is a closed-gate relaunch forge for turning a failed launch into proof, assets, and a safer next move.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:15.000
The repo already holds the core proof: a local entity package, logo seed dataset, and tool contracts.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:22.500
It also includes a launch draft, manual X thread drafts, and verifiers that keep money actions closed until human approval.

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:30.000
This is not a public launch claim. It is a private review surface for captions, transcript, chapter copy, and proof paths.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:37.500
Every risky lane stays off by default: no GPU run, no training, no paid API, and no livestream.

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:45.000
No private-media upload, checkout link, outreach, revenue claim, or affiliation claim is enabled.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:52.500
The next human step is to run the verifier, open the proof page, and review the captions against the final video.

00:00:52.500 --> 00:01:00.000
Only an awake operator can approve or reject a manual upload after checking the exact release text and media.
